 noreferrer"><time datetime="2019-05-16T06:50:50-07:00">05/16/2019 at 6:50 am</time></a></div><!-- .comment-metadata --></footer><!-- .comment-meta --><div class="comment-content"><p>Ok I just HAVE to comment on the first part of this post. Lauryn, YES I TOTALLY agree!!! I&#8217;m a barista, and it is so damn refreshing when someone just comes in like &#8220;hi hello I would please like this and this like this with this thank you!&#8221; It can be so draining to serve people who are rude and have no idea what they want and/or are HYPER apologetic about asking for modifications / whatever. You&#8217;re the best!</p></div><!-- .comment-content --><div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-996769" data-commentid="996769" data-postid="70749" data-belowelement="div-comment-996769" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Alexa" aria-label="Reply to Alexa">Reply</a></div></article><!-- .comment-body --></li><!-- #comment-## --><li id="comment-996771" class="comment even thread-even depth-1"><article id="div-comment-996771" class="comment-body"><footer class="comment-meta"><div class="comment-author vcard"> <img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8408da2fb204bc66316923e5db9f40e8f90aa1f6c8900711263a24659da996d4?s=60&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8408da2fb204bc66316923e5db9f40e8f90aa1f6c8900711263a24659da996d4?s=120&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg 2x' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/> <b class="fn"><a href="https://daysofkate.com/" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow" data-wpel-link="external">Kate</a></b> <span class="says">says:</span></div><!-- .comment-author --><div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.theskinnyconfidential.com/the-skinny-confidential-margarita/#comment-996771" data-wpel-link="internal" rel="follow noopener noreferrer"><time datetime="2019-05-16T06:57:19-07:00">05/16/2019 at 6:57 am</time></a></div><!-- .comment-metadata --></footer><!-- .comment-meta --><div class="comment-content"><p>This sounds so yummy!! Thanks for sharing, hope you&#8217;re having a great day.</p><p>-Kate<br /> https://daysofkate.com/</p></div><!-- .comment-content --><div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-996771" data-commentid="996771" data-postid="70749" data-belowelement="div-comment-996771" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Kate" aria-label="Reply to Kate">Reply</a></div></article><!-- .comment-body --></li><!-- #comment-## --><li id="comment-996788" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1"><article id="div-comment-996788" class="comment-body"><footer class="comment-meta"><div class="comment-author vcard"> <img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1157e9a3a940e5768fea1e59118ab1fb3abdd0741067a51ddd9c9e420a7569cd?s=60&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1157e9a3a940e5768fea1e59118ab1fb3abdd0741067a51ddd9c9e420a7569cd?s=120&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg 2x' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/> <b class="fn">tara</b> <span class="says">says:</span></div><!-- .comment-author --><div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.theskinnyconfidential.com/the-skinny-confidential-margarita/#comment-996788" data-wpel-link="internal" rel="follow noopener noreferrer"><time datetime="2019-05-16T11:47:26-07:00">05/16/2019 at 11:47 am</time></a></div><!-- .comment-metadata --></footer><!-- .comment-meta --><div class="comment-content"><p>i would like this to be my life motto:  just because im specific and know what i want does not mean im a bitch.  this applies to margs, to the f ing mess of a situation i have with a contractor over my patio right now, to the person at the store who when you ask &#8220;do you have X&#8221; says &#8220;no but we have Y&#8221;&#8230;.i want X lady !  Y is clearly an awful substitute are you nuts ?, and on and on !  Thank you for reminding me its ok to know what you want.  gotta love in the same scenario men are labeled decisive while women are demanding and bitchy !</p></div><!-- .comment-content --><div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-996788" data-commentid="996788" data-postid="70749" data-belowelement="div-comment-996788" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to tara" aria-label="Reply to tara">Reply</a></div></article><!-- .comment-body --></li><!-- #comment-## --><li id="comment-1066091" class="comment even thread-even depth-1"><article id="div-comment-1066091" class="comment-body"><footer class="comment-meta"><div class="comment-author vcard"> <img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1b36aecb92342b7003c721c579b9f4f9aff9e914f69ca5dc4fb3c20ab3045ed9?s=60&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1b36aecb92342b7003c721c579b9f4f9aff9e914f69ca5dc4fb3c20ab3045ed9?s=120&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg 2x' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/> <b class="fn">Nancy</b> <span class="says">says:</span></div><!-- .comment-author --><div class="comment-metadata"> <a href="https://www.theskinnyconfidential.com/the-skinny-confidential-margarita/#comment-1066091" data-wpel-link="internal" rel="follow noopener noreferrer"><time datetime="2020-01-30T13:05:46-08:00">01/30/2020 at 1:05 pm</time></a></div><!-- .comment-metadata --></footer><!-- .comment-meta --><div class="comment-content"><p>Come to Texas! New Braunfels is the greatest place. It’s between Austin and San Antonio. Come to the Huisache Grill and Bar. We don’t have mixed drinks but a great selection of wine! Ask for me I would be soooo happy to meet you! Great food too.<br /> Love y’all Nancy</p></div><!-- .comment-content --><div class="reply"><a rel="nofollow" class="comment-reply-link" href="#comment-1066091" data-commentid="1066091" data-postid="70749" data-belowelement="div-comment-1066091" data-respondelement